description: Gog is a fictional character, a comic book supervillain in the Marvel Comics Universe. Created by writer Roy Thomas and Gil Kane, the character first appears in The Amazing Spider-Man #103.An alien being from an unknown planet, Gog resembles a gigantic reptilian humanoid; despite his monstrous appearance and demeanor, Gog is actually quite intelligent, capable of understanding human speech and creating various complex devices.
name: Gog
